    "IntroductionLearning disabilities or learning disorders, a hypernym for a wide variety of learning problems hinders the skill acquisition activity of an individual.",
    "It is not a problem with intelligence.",
    "Nevertheless, it can have a negative impact on the self-esteem and confidence of children who are expected to acquire new information and skills day by day.",
    "Students with learning disabilities account for the major proportion of the \"special educational needs\" category [1].",
    "Since these disabilities affect the perception capability of a child, the difficulties may be either in reading, writing, doing math, or any other tasks."
